{"tid":220803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［分餅仔］游蕙禎獲哈佛史丹佛青睞","createTime":"2017-04-28T08:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T05:46:28.000Z","uid":389,"like":10,"dislike":130,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"115794a9a761d371682d68b057cfc4306f5da39b","tid":220803,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"立法會議辦清場當日，房內留下大量酒樽，當人以為梁游嗜酒，其實從新聞片段，會發現另一真相，游使用酒精催生魔髮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hVdh9pw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhVdh9pw.jpg&h=40c61fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前Reuters訪問，游戴上畫家帽，表面是文青打扮，實際上：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04eVs3P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04eVs3P.jpg&h=46b64ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6AXo18D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6AXo18D.jpg&h=20e5fa23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以看見災情嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n人的髮質有異，游並非脫髮，但天生髮輪附近毛孔分散，於是有脫髮的錯覺。但對女生而言，總有尷尬之處，加上早前曾公開與陳雲劃清界線，表示從未受教於陳雲。其用意所在，除禁止陳雲再借游為他學生之名招搖撞騙，在吸引力法則下，亦有可能不想被陳雲地中海感染。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/993FVBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F993FVBC.jpg&h=6ee4c733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖：三名脫髮人士，攝於青山醫院）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2pk77W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2pk77W.jpg&h=d833c2d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烈酒生髮，可參考喬寶寶訪問，稱自己多毛是因為小時候用白蘭地塗抹身體。<br />\n<br />\n當黃台仰要留學劍橋養老時，也許游蕙禎心中有另一個哈佛夢？其實也有史丹佛美髮學苑"},{"pid":"cf5ff31ee51cd7c47eaa88805b35b3a2508d17ba","tid":220803,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"作新聞？"},{"pid":"3358d5750b390a93be94f972a4907ca602c6efc3","tid":220803,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:36:43.000Z","msg":"你up乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b559bc625496